# Git and version control
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# Environment and secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# IDE and editor files
**/.vscode
**/.vs
**/.idea
**/.project
**/.settings
**/.classpath
**/.toolstarget

# Node.js
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log
**/yarn-debug.log
**/yarn-error.log
**/.npm
**/.yarn
**/package-lock.json.bak

# Build artifacts
**/dist
**/build
**/obj
**/*.dbmdl
**/*.jfm
**/*.*proj.user

# Test and coverage
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/.playwright

# Logs
**/logs
**/*.log

# Docker files (don't copy into image)
**/Dockerfile*
**/docker-compose*
**/compose*
**/.dockerignore

# Documentation (save space, keep essential docs in image)
README.md
LICENSE
CHANGELOG.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
*.md
!DEPLOYMENT-GUIDE.md
!QUICK-START.md

# Charts and diagrams
**/charts

# Secrets and sensitive files
**/secrets.dev.yaml
**/values.dev.yaml
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.crt
**/*.pfx

# Temporary files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.tmp
**/*.swp
**/*.bak
**/*.old

# Test and demo apps (not needed in production)
**/test-demo-app

# GitHub workflows (not needed in container)
**/.github
